Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:08.83,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,...so the least I can do is squash a fleeing bug like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:10.83,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Recall that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:15.21,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Recall the essence of cursed energy \Nyou seized back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:18.84,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Bad aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.31,0:21:29.18,Default,Kugisaki,0,0,0,,Hairpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:39.11,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:42.24,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,But that simply won't work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:47.24,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\i1}Judging from what she said, she must be close to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:54.04,Default,Mahito,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,0)\i1}I'll drag her corpse before Itadori Yuji and break his soul!
